{"id":"concepts/first-generation-guilt","title":"First-generation guilt","type":"concepts","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. <em>\"How can I be sad when I have so many opportunities?\"</em> — the guilt-frame that binds Yahir's awareness of <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">Dad's</a> sacrifice (leaving <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/mexico\">Mexico</a>) to his own permission-to-feel. Surfaces when scholarship-essay registers (<a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-01-12-fhs-final\">FHS final</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-04-09-rudy-sanchez-scolarships\">scholarship grind</a>) collide with <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2023-05-05-happy-birthday-poem\">family grief writing</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Connects to <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/the-other-wes-moore\">Other Wes Moore</a> reading as a class-and-race version of the same mechanic — opportunity as inherited debt.</p>\n<p>Connections: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/dad-yahir\">dad yahir</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/mexico\">mexico</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/debt-of-gratitude\">debt of gratitude</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/college-admissions\">college admissions</a> · scholarship grind 2021</p>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2022-02-05-Al-Forthan-Email","label":"Al Forthan Scholarship Essay"},{"id":"concepts/college-admissions","label":"College admissions (Yahir, 2020–2021)"},{"id":"concepts/imposter-syndrome-cultural","label":"Cultural Imposter Syndrome"},{"id":"entities/dad-yahir","label":"Dad Yahir"},{"id":"concepts/debt-of-gratitude","label":"Debt of Gratitude"},{"id":"summaries/2021-01-12-fhs-final","label":"FHS final — The Other Wes Moore ecological-model essay (1/12/21)"},{"id":"summaries/2023-05-05-happy-birthday-poem","label":"Happy birthday poem (Feb 7th — Yahir & Dad)"},{"id":"entities/mexico","label":"Mexico"},{"id":"summaries/2021-04-09-rudy-sanchez-scolarships","label":"Rudy Sanchez scholarships list (4/9/21)"},{"id":"entities/the-other-wes-moore","label":"The Other Wes Moore (book)"}]}
